# Progress — 2026-05-21 18:41 (fast connect + Citrix UX)

## Completed
- **Fast connect**: `fast-connect.js` — 8s budget; recovery/watchdogs only after first frame (`video-recovery.js` `armWatchdogs`)
- **ICE discipline**: no restart when DTLS connected; reconnect after 10s failed/disconnected (`connection-manager.js`)
- **Startup quality**: `startup_mobile` preset (640×360, 8fps, 550k) → ramp via `quality-controller.js`
- **Pointer**: `pointer-controller.js` — persistent down/move/up, drag lock, right-click
- **Gestures**: tap/double-tap-hold lock, 2-finger scroll + tap right-click, pinch zoom (`gestures.js`, `viewport-controller.js`, `scroll-engine.js`)
- **Keyboard**: `#hidden-text` textarea bridge + clipboard paste (`keyboard-bridge.js`)
- **Toolbar**: floating translucent dock, auto-hide, clipboard/right-click/reconnect buttons

## Test (iPhone Safari)
1. Tap to Connect → first frame should hide splash within ~10s
2. Drag window (trackpad + hold), double-tap-hold drag lock
3. Two-finger scroll; two-finger tap right-click
4. Pinch zoom; paste via toolbar or ⌘V in keyboard field

# Progress — 2026-05-21 (video recovery)

## Safari video freeze recovery
- `video-recovery.js`: monitors currentTime, readyState, track state, black screen
- Escalation: soft play → refresh srcObject → host keyframe → hard reconnect
- Tab foreground + bfcache `pageshow` recovery
- HUD `vid:ok|frozen|recovering|black`
- Host handles `{t:"keyframe"}` per peer

# Progress — 2026-05-21 (production mobile)

## Phase 1 ICE/TURN
- Safari mobile: `iceTransportPolicy: "relay"` via `/ice-config` + `ice_policy.py`
- Relay-only SDP filter (offer + answer) when relay policy active
- TURN UDP/TCP/443/TLS in `ice_config.py`
- ICE diagnostics: selected_pair logs, platform meta, ICE duration
- Reconnect: exponential backoff 2s–30s, connect debounce, clientId dedup
- Stale peer GC (30s loop)
- Adaptive quality: `adapt` messages → bitrate/FPS on host

## Phase 2 Mobile UX
- Modular `client/js/*` (no monolithic client.js)
- Trackpad + direct touch modes (localStorage)
- Virtual cursor, gestures (scroll/pinch/3-finger keyboard)
- Mobile toolbar (collapsible, safe-area)
- Hidden input keyboard bridge
- HUD panel: RTT, loss, relay path, fps

## Phase 3 Backend
- `peer_manager.py` — offer handling, cleanup, dedup
- `peer_session.py` — extended state
- Mobile preset: 960×540 @ 10fps, 850kbps

## Test
1. `python host.py -v`
2. iPhone Safari → ngrok HTTPS, hard refresh
3. Console: `ICE policy relay`, `selected_pair=relay/...`
4. Trackpad mode + toolbar
